core:processNote.core:description:
This process manages a single thread within the MultiThreadedConfigurableQueueConsumer.
It calls the MultiThreadedFeeder process to move a message from the primary queue to a queue specific to this thread.
It then calls the QueueConsumer process to read back the message and handle it.
To support retry, the QueueConsumer is passed the MultiThreadedPayloadHandler process as the payload handler.

core:param.value: Failed to resolve primary queue name
core:param.name: enactor.coreUI.LogMessage
